# Add this file to your .vim folder and make it read only

Hotkeys:

SPACE - h - k                 : Show hotkeys
SPACE - v                     : Open .vimrc file
SPACE - g - d                 : Go to definition
SPACE - g - r                 : Go to reference
SPACE - t                     : Open terminal in a new window
CTRL - \ CTRL - n             : Exit terminal insert mode
SPACE - SPACE - p             : Format Prettier
SPACE - SPACE - g             : Format GoFmt
SPACE - SPACE - b             : Format Black
SPACE - SPACE - u             : Toggle UndoTree
SPACE - SPACE - f             : Find Files (FZF & RIPGREP)
Control - p                   : Git files (git ls-files)
CTRL - -                      : Comment or Uncomment line
<F6>                          : Toggle NERDTree
SPACE - 1                     : Go to next buffer in list 
SPACE - 2                     : Go to prev buffer in list 
SPACE - h                     : Move cursor to window on the left
SPACE - j                     : Move cursor to window on the down
SPACE - k                     : Move cursor to window on the up 
SPACE - l                     : Move cursor to window on the right
SPACE - =                     : Expand window
SPACE - -                     : Shrink window
